{"about_the_game":"WARNING: If you are playing this game for the first time, please be aware that you may find the game difficult and may require repeated failures.<br><br>'Hide Alone' is a first-person survival horror game where you survive for a limited time.<br>It is a story that takes place when the protagonist, who is usually interested in supernatural phenomena, becomes interested in the dangerous game of hide and seek, which can only be played at 3 am.<br>This dangerous game requires no one in the house and only you and your doll play hide and seek.<br>At 3am the doll comes to life, and you have to turn off all the lights and rely on your lighter in the dark.<br>There are rules to follow when playing hide-and-seek, and breaking even one of these rules can put your life at risk.<br>Therefore, you will need to familiarize yourself with the rules and be careful not to get caught by them.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>HAUNTED DOLL</u></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/allen.gif?t=1734016310\" /><br>When hide and seek begins, a haunted doll will wander around looking for you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>FIND ITEM</u></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/item.gif?t=1734016310\" /><br>You will have to find the items you need to survive in the dark.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>CURSING GIRL</u></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/ally.gif?t=1734016310\" /><br>The girl who curses you will keep following you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>FOLLOW THE RULES</u></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/rules.gif?t=1734016310\" /><br>If you want to finish hide and seek safely, you must follow the rules.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2024300?t=